00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:48,730
Father!

55
00:03:49,630 --> 00:03:50,260
Father!

56
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:53,600
Come here, darling.

57
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:54,540
فتاة طيبة.

58
